OL,12,G1730FFilm Noir
OL,13,     GClassic Noir. 2022. The 1940s and
OL,14,     G50s were the heyday of Film Noir.
OL,15,     GThis new style which had
OL,16,     Gdeveloped from the days of silent
OL,17,     Gfilm and German Expressionism was
OL,18,     Gnow reaching its peak in
OL,19,     GHollywood.
